{"tid":577303,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來我食過人","createTime":"2018-03-01T15:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T20:12:04.000Z","uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f180faa92e986a96945f8aea4d52165cc6e1682","tid":577303,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"我老母同我講我細細食過好多胎盤，話醫哮喘，有冇人食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b67aa69b4273dc44ab805ce05dace5887afa424","tid":577303,"uid":46943,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"胎盤都叫人<br />\n不如咬指甲都係啦"},{"pid":"e8dd3a42e49839b3a32b0d2a9c56a4b687d33534","tid":577303,"uid":100730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"其實我認為，社會普遍意義上嘅「人食人」禁忌，除咗「食用」呢個行為本身，好大程度仲取決喺「準備食材」呢個過程。公眾判斷一個人食用人體組織本身係咪「食緊人」，好多時候係睇食嘅人本身有無殺死或者傷害過其他人&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;或者咁講，有無破壞到社會風俗。而「食人」本身只係附帶嘅事件，對公眾而言，其實係謀殺等影響社會安定嘅行為對前者嘅傷害比較重要。<br />\n<br />\n照我嘅睇法，「食人」係大眾嘅觀點嚟講只係一種獵奇事件，人真正驚嘅其實係食人所導致嘅謀殺行為本身，仲有對死者安寧被打擾嘅恐懼。<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9ea5f003b6472b8c854b5d8d0eba2db92c2338","tid":577303,"uid":31521,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/001923_26d45b4eb2a4a0dc116bbcd2a1610ffa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F001923_26d45b4eb2a4a0dc116bbcd2a1610ffa.png&h=19774fbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"787678ead5e1eadf61fe6abbaee1fcc05933589a","tid":577303,"uid":169655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"開心大發現"},{"pid":"0bca7d283d4a60711ca626ffb5b81649b555c470","tid":577303,"uid":129521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"哪來的胎盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}